    "value": "b is an object aggregate means: b is a material entity consisting exactly of a plurality of objects as member_parts at all times at which b exists. (axiom label in BFO2 Reference: [025-004])"
  },
  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000602": {
    "axioms": [
      {
        "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0010000": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/bfo/axiom/025-004"
      }
    ],
    "type": [
      "reification"
    ],
    "value": "(forall (x) (if (ObjectAggregate x) (and (MaterialEntity x) (forall (t) (if (existsAt x t) (exists (y z) (and (Object y) (Object z) (memberPartOfAt y x t) (memberPartOfAt z x t) (not (= y z)))))) (not (exists (w t_1) (and (memberPartOfAt w x t_1) (not (Object w)))))))) // axiom label in BFO2 CLIF: [025-004] "
  },
